from fading too fast? ♪
so thank you.

28:58.070 --> 29:00.838
Because i know...

29:00.840 --> 29:02.272
And i'm sorry.

29:07.780 --> 29:10.047
You think you can just
apologize to me

29:10.049 --> 29:12.116
