of new things to say? ♪
[ sighs ]

29:28.868 --> 29:32.870
What have you ever sacrificed
for me, fitz?

29:32.872 --> 29:38.041
♪ and since we know
we're always changing ♪

29:38.043 --> 29:40.978
You are going to be
the first woman

29:40.980 --> 29:42.546
To put her hand
on the bible

29:42.548 --> 29:44.448
In front of
the capitol building

29:44.450 --> 29:46.383
And be sworn in...
[ sighs ]

29:46.385 --> 29:49.453
...As president of the
united states of america.

29:49.455 --> 29:52.022
I believe that

29:52.024 --> 29:54.424
