29:58.297 --> 30:00.364
I don't have your will.

30:02.101 --> 30:06.470
And that must feel like
an awful betrayal.

30:06.472 --> 30:12.342
♪ i know the way
i feel for you ♪

30:12.344 --> 30:13.911
♪ it's now or never ♪

30:13.913 --> 30:15.279
[ sighs ]

30:15.281 --> 30:21.018
♪ the more i love,
the more that i'm afraid ♪

30:21.020 --> 30:23.520
[ sighs ] i thought we would
grow old together.

30:23.522 --> 30:25.022
I know.

30:25.024 --> 30:27.024
♪ that in your arms
i may not see forever ♪

30:27.026 --> 30:29.092
[ sighs ] me too.

30:29.094 --> 30:32.162
♪ forever ♪

