Oh.
I-i was looking for --

31:02.361 --> 31:05.028
He's in the oval,
getting ready for the interview.

31:05.030 --> 31:07.531
Oh, okay. Thanks.

31:07.533 --> 31:10.167
Abby.

31:10.169 --> 31:12.903
I'm sorry i lied to you.

31:14.874 --> 31:18.342
I'm just not used
to any of this.

31:18.344 --> 31:21.211
I mean, in any other situation,
i would be --

31:21.213 --> 31:23.380
Me. You'd be me.

31:25.284 --> 31:27.217
Yeah.

31:28.287 --> 31:32.022
[ sighs ]

