from the best in the business.

31:54.513 --> 31:55.379
[ chuckles ]

31:57.549 --> 32:00.083
Thanks, kyle.

32:00.085 --> 32:02.686
Thanks.
[ breathes deeply ]

32:02.688 --> 32:05.989
Sir, i hope i didn't
overstep earlier,

32:05.991 --> 32:09.559
