35:10.342 --> 35:11.875
Get everything
you asked for?

35:11.877 --> 35:14.211
'cause i don't think
you did.

35:14.213 --> 35:15.812
I don't think anything
is different

35:15.814 --> 35:19.382
Than it was when you stood
in this room

35:19.384 --> 35:21.551
And told me that
you should've gotten more.

35:21.553 --> 35:23.186
[ breathes deeply ]

35:23.188 --> 35:24.221
Did that happen?

35:24.223 --> 35:26.456
Did he give you more?

35:26.458 --> 35:28.492
Did he give you anything?

35:28.494 --> 35:30.794
After all the times,
all the years,

35:30.796 --> 35:32.762
All the lies,

35:32.764 --> 35:35.499
