36:39.698 --> 36:41.631
<i> He didn't just</i>
<i> sneeze one day and die.</i>

36:41.633 --> 36:42.766
And i didn't always
say thank you,

36:42.768 --> 36:44.585
But deep down,
i knew how i got here.

36:44.586 --> 36:46.403
<i> He died so that we could</i>
<i> stay in this white house</i>
<i> for four more years.</i>

36:46.405 --> 36:47.537
<i> He died for our sins.</i>

36:47.539 --> 36:49.673
So, thank you.
Because i know...

36:49.675 --> 36:51.792
And i'm sorry.

36:51.793 --> 36:53.910
Mellie:
<i> You take everything from me!</i>

36:53.912 --> 36:56.947
